STORY low    PRIORITY 1.
STORY high   PRIORITY 3.
STORY medium PRIORITY 2.
ACTION run.
EVENT spotted ENVIRONMENT.
DURING ALWAYS:
    WHEN spotted ENVIRONMENT:
        DO run.
DURING low:
    WHEN spotted ENVIRONMENT:
        DO run.
DURING medium:
    WHEN spotted ENVIRONMENT:
        DO run.
DURING high:
    WHEN spotted ENVIRONMENT:
        DO run.
